data.message:
**Welcome to the GolmiEval Task!** Describe the highlighted piece on the board on the 
right so that another person could **uniquely** identify it. 
When in doubt, click on a piece to find out if that's your target.
The blue piece above the brown piece on the left side, below the green reversed-L-shaped piece, right to the blue Z-shaped piece
The yellow piece above the blue piece on the left side, below the purple piece on the left side, right next to the yellow piece
The brown cross shaped piece on the red rectangle piece, above two brown cross shaped pieces
The blue horizontal piece below the blue cross-shaped piece, left to the yellow piece
The red L-shaped piece above the pink piece, left to the red T-shaped piece
Still 10 boards to go
The orange horizontal piece above the green cross-shaped piece
The light blue piece above the light blue L-shaped piece, left to the light blue Z-shaped piece
The orange piece on the right side, above two orange pieces
The brown piece above a blue piece and below blue, brown, and dark blue pieces
The brown reversed-T-shaped piece below the light blue piece and right next to the purple piece
Still 5 boards to go. You almost made it!
The blue piece left to the red piece and above two blue pieces
The yellow cross-shaped piece above a light blue piece, below a green piece, and right to two green pieces
The blue Z-shaped piece above the light blue L-shaped piece and right to the gray piece
The brown piece between gray and pink pieces, below a yellow piece
The pink piece left to a dark blue piece, right to a brown piece, and below orange and brown pieces
That was the last one 🎉 🎉 thank you very much for your time! I really appreciate your help.
The room is closing, see you next time 👋
